<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7626227>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21. A–D, Mithraculus forceps A. Milne-Edwards, 1875.A, Male MZUSP 33739, cl 11.8 mm, cw 13.5 mm. B, Ovigerous female (MZUSP 40602), cl 11.9 mm, cw 13.4 mm. C, Ovigerous female (MZUSP 40568), cl 8.5 mm, cw 9.5 mm. D, Juvenile female (MZUSP 40245), cl 5.8 mm, cw 6.2 mm. Habitus, dorsal (A, C, D) and ventral (B) view. Photographs by A. Pol." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7626227/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7626235>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. A–G, Teleophrys pococki Rathbun, 1924. A, Adult male (MZUSP 39583), cl 9.2 mm, cw 10 mm. B, Ovigerous female (MZUSP 40614), cl 7.8 mm, cw 8 mm. C, D, Ovigerous female (MZUSP 39687), cl 6.1 mm, cw 6.1 mm. E, Juvenile male (MZUSP 40699), cl 4.1 mm, cw 4 mm. Note the more granular carapace and spiniform anterolateral teeth. F, G, Juvenile" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7626235/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

